ments and extensions of some known results. Moreover, we will apply\nthese results to several well-known inequalities such as\nHardy--Littlewood--Sobolev and Olsen-type inequalities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Dec 2022 03:46:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-02"}
