ightful results supporting the\ntransformation of traditional universities into sustainable, fourth-generation\nhigher education institutions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Dec 2022 09:14:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-04"}
